Cold-Hearted and Efficient	KEY:PFS Scenario 9-18 ~ Cold-Hearted and Efficient	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Chronicle_S09-18.PFSBoon	VISIBLE:YES	COST:0	DESC:Your heart was unmoved by the desperate plight of Dolok Darkfur, and you chose to leave the former god of the Farheavens to his misery. You can activate this boon as a standard action to gain a +2 bonus on all saving throws against emotion effects for 10 minutes. In addition, if you are currently affected by an emotion effect when you activate this boon, you can immediately attempt a new saving throw against that effect, adding the bonus from this boon to the result. When you use this boon, cross it off your Chronicle sheet.
